videos.description: The Nets have no trouble moving the ball around the perimeter as Kevin Durant is left wide open for a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Nets' ball movement leads to an easy 3 for Durant) 2021/1/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nets' ball movement leads to an easy 3 for Durant

videos.description: DeAndre Jordan throws down a monster dunk in the lane, then blocks Russell Westbrook on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jordan throws down hammer jam, blocks Westbrook) 2021/1/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan throws down hammer jam, blocks Westbrook

videos.description: Kevin Durant flies for a massive dunk that puts Davis Bertans on a poster in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant takes off for poster jam on Bertans) 2021/1/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant takes off for poster jam on Bertans

videos.description: Bradley Beal crashes into the lane for two points as the Wizards grab their first lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beal drives through lane for tough basket) 2021/1/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beal drives through lane for tough basket

videos.description: Russell Westbrook and Bruce Brown are given a double technical in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook given another technical foul after exchanging words with Nets guard) 2021/1/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook given another technical foul after exchanging words with Nets guard

videos.description: After Bradley Beal drains a 3-pointer, the Wizards get a steal and pass to Russell Westbrook, who drains another 3 to give Washington a lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beal, Westbrook drain late 3s seconds apart to give Wizards lead) 2021/1/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beal, Westbrook drain late 3s seconds apart to give Wizards lead

videos.description: Timothe Luwawu-Cabarrot has a great look at the go-ahead layup, but his shot just rolls out to all but seal the Wizards' comeback.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Nets' game-winning layup attempt just rolls out) 2020/01/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nets' game-winning layup attempt just rolls out

videos.description: Down five with under 10 seconds to go, Bradley Beal and Russell Westbrook hit clutch 3-pointers as the Wizards stun the Nets in regulation.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Beal, Westbrook lead Wizards' remarkable comeback vs. Nets) 2021/1/31 ESHEET SVP

videos.headline: Beal, Westbrook lead Wizards' remarkable comeback vs. Nets

videos.description: Russell Westbrook gives his game-worn sneakers to an arena worker after the Wizards defeated the Nets.
